   * </td></tr>
   * <tr><td>
   *
   * `void beforeFragment`
   *
   * </td><td>
   *
   * Called at the start of the fragment shader.
   *
   * </td></tr>
   * <tr><td>
   *
   * `Inputs getPixelInputs`
   *
